me":"2019-08-01T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oJD83L9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoJD83L9.png&h=f594d73c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pXkrQra.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpXkrQra.png&h=fa896eab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEWCcEw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEWCcEw.png&h=77349953&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34fe9c3fb58d225513d3c28865e272c40d5e1a07","tid":1393962,"uid":59511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"On9,罷工唔係自願嘅根本就冇力量，玩多幾日仲會流失埋中間嘅民意。"},{"pid":"4e673a5afd7fc476e5a0e8a5379d7df55bde8253","tid":1393962,"uid":156254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:54:29.000Z","msg":"搵一大堆人塞起&quot;某個MTR&quot; 站出口<br />\n咁未要被迫關閘囉"},{"pid":"4c803b69607ee018a0d465a4a84db1b6ace6086b","tid":1393962,"uid":131731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"感謝巴打<br />\n85齊罷工企出黎"},{"pid":"e8dd2f8f5004b8d8cce405abc6af811488181a42","tid":1393962,"uid":260262,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:56:39.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n6月個陣有個港豬fd仲同我講遊行冇用 但罷工佢就支持<br />\n講呢句已經開始嘈緊佢<br />\n問佢罷工個日會做咩 佢答我：唔需要同你講<br />\n唔敢講罷工留係屋企打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但又唔想比我屌<br />\n所以大家 罷工請出黎<br />\n咁先係真係做到野 而唔係藉罷工休息"},{"pid":"95f929a6dff4971e5a789e5f6b7707912eacd83a","tid":1393962,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023e2b962443dea6310ce0d79fa297d005809d5e","tid":1393962,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d297d16a9c1ed2627bb7a1ccf14e4387fdc43c4e","tid":1393962,"uid":61615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:04:20.000Z","msg":"8月5 我罷工"},{"pid":"d8fb3c6151433f6de534e00b7428a956265ffa57","tid":1393962,"uid":207071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34fe9c3fb58d225513d3c28865e272c40d5e1a07","tid":1393962,"uid":59511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"On9,罷工唔係自願嘅根本就冇力量，玩多幾日仲會流失埋中間嘅民意。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:04:41.000Z","msg":"無人知8月5會發生咩事 <br />\n可能因為8月5 有長期罷工<br />\n亦都可能係一日罷工<br />\n但係如果一日都唔肯付出 <br />\n咁仲講咩革命 講咩民主"},{"pid":"d87e868400f5b4b55d9787cde83e71beaf511714","tid":1393962,"uid":286884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:05:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afdaf3d547b789dbab2d965120c98e62c7f1bbff","tid":1393962,"uid":217164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:05:20.000Z","msg":"8月5不合作運動同罷工正式上線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cec499854648fef67a5053912234ec10abaeac9","tid":1393962,"uid":192754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"True"},{"pid":"3fc7c22ab227d781c28fb0722e27827fe1834eda","tid":1393962,"uid":77034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"會計界朋友、同事，攜手爲香港出一分力。5/8 請假、病假、罷工。<br />\n<br />\n[會計師] 5/8 工作安排 入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQcmCra.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQcmCra.png&h=561c6d53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kbAn6jw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkbAn6jw.png&h=2638407a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/syj0SZx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsyj0SZx.png&h=a3a9efc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nmRKAcS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnmRKAcS.png&h=ccaca3ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VxkLjEy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxkLjEy.png&h=73508860&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewGRZEy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FewGRZEy.png&h=0adfc7b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07k3QMf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07k3QMf.png&h=7e385604&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c947b8c31b5b82099ba744f024695dab56fd8e5b","tid":1393962,"uid":146390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:07:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ac9129ec5f9c7bda6193575c5093285fc8a08d08","tid":1393962,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b29052a1ddf518ed3f7ba9daa5240fa6eeb525f","tid":1393962,"uid":207071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"8月5大罷工  大家唔好諗住請日假係屋企會有用<br />\n政府係唔會理你地 。<br />\n<br />\n香港人好被動 唔會主動抗爭，同時亦唔係好多人做到罷工呢樣野 ，大家都有好多藉口請唔到假<br />\n咩供樓 得罪上司 乜乜柒柒咁。<br />\n<br />\n但係如果我地可以令到佢地都搭唔到車 <br />\n咁就可以令到今次罷工發揮到最大既效用<br />\n因為唔係佢地主動唔返工 而係返唔到工<br />\n<br />\n公務員就係最被動既香港人 <br />\n因為佢地做又36唔做又36 <br />\n大家都好想公務員一齊join今次罷工 <br />\n唔知你地知唔知 大部份高級既公務員<br />\n都係藍絲 所以上一次612有罷既公務員 <br />\n其實已經好叻<br />\n好多人都係諗住 返到咪返到 返唔到咪由佢囉。<br />\n<br />\n如果我地8月5可以做到全港塞車 巴士 地鐵都行唔到<br />\n咁先至係最work既罷工<br />\n我地唔能夠改變人地既想法 但係行為上 可以令到佢地被動咁罷工。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會已經提左我地唔好圍巴士總站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剩低既大家要努力 唔好怪責啲罷唔到工既公務員 <br />\n其實佢地好多都係企係市民呢邊<br />\n<br />\n最後同咁多位想輕生既人講 垃圾政府係唔會理你地 你見之前啲學生因為學業問題跳樓 政府講咩？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「你地啲後生唔知咩叫辛苦 我地之前咪又係咁 」</span><br />\n如果你地有死既覺悟 倒不如去直線幫手。<br />\n<br />\nLe vent se l&egrave;ve，il faut tenter de vivre。<br />\n風起了，但我們仍要努力地 生存下去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSYpBRk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSYpBRk.png&h=31826bd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我呢邊最早返08:15 最遲09:00 <br />\n<br />\n#不割席<br />\n#不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n咁多位 聽日見！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:07:23.000Z","msg":"其實mtr成班人個個坐到總站先落車已經可以合法玩死mtr"},{"pid":"b1d615d734fa9a0f4bf1af831abf9bc0a32f456c","tid":1393962,"uid":124910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:08:21.000Z","msg":"塞路要同時係巴士站地鐵站做文宣/放映/演講"},{"pid":"173b1abf415bb045808ab988751bac33db159fde","tid":1393962,"uid":124910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:08:31.000Z","msg":"塞路要同時係巴士站地鐵站做文宣/放映/演講"},{"pid":"6ea7e64a5be690278b8d85aede8a6c3ec74cfd31","tid":1393962,"uid":124910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:08:42.000Z","msg":"塞路要同時係巴士站地鐵站做文宣/放映/演講"},{"pid":"4a9c3ea79e58c9693125d528b4f54f75cc102fb6","tid":1393962,"uid":187796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:09:20.000Z","msg":"我會罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d54e3ef095142d90bd8807e2ba51bcaa90310e","tid":1393962,"uid":293368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:09:36.000Z","msg":"罷工撘地鐵遊車河"},{"pid":"3e8790f1d946c2aecca2e5c219099e063f00c6ab","tid":1393962,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"如果罷完政府都係強烈譴責個堆廢話可以點做"},{"pid":"6adc83657cdfa95fadd61989c83de4638657a680","tid":1393962,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:10:20.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"098c518be03d99a3cb81bd2316ff34baedeeff09","tid":1393962,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:10:28.000Z","msg":"去七區集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1a71e24248763457c64468833de113b5adb6f4","tid":1393962,"uid":262340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:11:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"875708d6026e3f0001ab5a552bbf6c52476b2ab6","tid":1393962,"uid":262340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591e6d29003051aca1d61569b5420a72b823aac6","tid":1393962,"uid":947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:11:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6869f6fc7dca8a4d182190c3e384ecf58ca9191","tid":1393962,"uid":39081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:12:47.000Z","msg":"令到其他人返唔到工<br />\n係無任何意義<br />\n因為佢地唔係自願<br />\n而係被逼<br />\n<br />\n罷工 最大嘅力量<br />\n係呢班人自願企出嚟<br />\n表達自己嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n三思呀"},{"pid":"5acd83abc884d6433b2df0d24bf7f5d3fc7e0344","tid":1393962,"uid":120729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:13:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01af859a03d42644a8312027eeabca71d039d80b","tid":1393962,"uid":281533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:14:56.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ae2239d9bac93d53819839b2e84f717257fd1639","tid":1393962,"uid":226592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157e5297b1a5fbb44e2f8627e5e1f41927e6228b","tid":1393962,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a989cb72b5409ad0d7a0571f21522dd8d0222fa2","tid":1393962,"uid":39081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8fb3c6151433f6de534e00b7428a956265ffa57","tid":139