鐵行動會咁大爭議？<br />\n因為規模未夠大<br />\n每次都只係塞一條線  其他地區打工仔心諗點解唔過黎幫我罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nthat's why 要一次全面性塞過海線+3隧既大規模行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如何合法癱瘓港鐵</span><br />\n一人一喼港鐵fashion show大賽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390849</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:24:35.000Z","msg":"塞港鐵有個大問題<br />\n就係 有d人返到工有人返唔到<br />\n要做到人人都返唔到 老細都返唔到<br />\n咁樣先有用"},{"pid":"1e21986491b9cdf3d1dcb5712a61765a60bc4457","tid":1393962,"uid":152571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"風起了，我要努力活下去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088925ce679de89018700f287b1790ed135593b4","tid":1393962,"uid":238525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:25:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a72d854acbaad9a09fcbd077d01b425731266daa","tid":1393962,"uid":244509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:26:48.000Z","msg":"[義士安家費]二百萬人, 每人只要捐100蚊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1394100/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1394100/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[智能燈柱]聽人講想係用大麻繩綁住燈柱, 玩街頭拔河大賽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1393989/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1393989/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n不合作運動 - 查狗牌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1394054/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1394054/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bcbf1ca38ac4843519707f6c20e3a8d82abf5fea","tid":1393962,"uid":279895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im